session.content: Hello there! I'm glad you reached out. How can I assist you today? I'm here to listen and help as best I can. Could you please tell me more about what's been going on with your health recently? Are there any specific symptoms or concerns that have been bothering you? It would be helpful if we could discuss the timing, severity, and any red flags you might have noticed. If it helps, feel free to describe the symptoms in as much detail as possible so I can better understand how they're affecting you.

I'm really sorry to hear that you've been experiencing a headache. To help me provide the best advice, could you please tell me more about your headache? For instance, is it a continuous or intermittent headache? Does it occur on one side of your head or all over? Do you feel any specific pain intensity, from mild to severe? Also, have you noticed any other symptoms accompanying the headache like nausea, vomiting, vision changes, speech difficulties, or weakness in any part of your body? This information will help me understand better and provide guidance on what could be causing it.

triage.reason: No red flags found; symptoms appear non-urgent.
